Application: Embroidr
Author: W4g3n3r

Embroidr hopes to be a friendly file manager for large libraries of digital ebroidery files. 

The initial release will include the following features:
	-Support for .pes (Brother) files.
	-Viewing the ebroidery design.
	-Saving the design as an svg file.
	-Tagging files for easier management.
	-Ability to search files.
	-Automatic file extraction from zip files.
	-Automatic file indexing.
	-A plugin api for easily adding more embroidery formats.
	-Automatic file organization.
